request.description:
Method: POST
URL: {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/jobs/cancel
Auth: Admin access token with jobs:cancel permission
Body: TargetType vehicle|market|stall, TargetRef, optional WorkerAction and reason. For vehicle, WorkerAction defaults to requeue and returns cancelled workers to the front of the queue in assignment accept order. Use open_app only when admin does not want to return workers to queue. For market/stall, omit WorkerAction or send none.
Examples:
Vehicle requeue: { "TargetType": "vehicle", "TargetRef": "{{ticketNo}}" }
Vehicle open_app: { "TargetType": "vehicle", "TargetRef": "{{ticketNo}}", "WorkerAction": "open_app" }
Market: { "TargetType": "market", "TargetRef": "{{marketCode}}" }
Stall: { "TargetType": "stall", "TargetRef": "{{boothCode}}" }

